BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-07-19T03:30:00&endDate=2026-07-19T09:15:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWEAVER LINE: Sunday 19 July\, until 1015\, no service between Liverpool Street and Cheshunt / Chingford / Enfield Town. Use London Underground or London Buses via any reasonable route. \r\n\r\nRail replacement buses will run as follows: Service L1: Seven Sisters - Bruce Grove - White Hart Lane - Silver Street - Edmonton Green - Bush Hill Park - Enfield Town\; Service L2: Seven Sisters - Bruce Grove - White Hart Lane - Silver Street - Edmonton Green - Bush Hill Park - Southbury - Turkey Street - Theobalds Grove - Cheshunt\; Service L3: Hackney Downs - Clapton - St. James Street - Walthamstow Central - Wood Street - Highams Park - Chingford. \r\n\r\nFirst trains: Enfield Town to Liverpool Street 09:57\; Liverpool Street to Enfield Town 10:20\; First Liverpool Street to Cheshunt 10:12\; Cheshunt to Liverpool Street 10:01\; Liverpool Street to Chingford 10:02\; Chingford to Liverpool Street 10:08
DTEND:20260719T091500Z
DTSTART:20260719T033000Z
SUMMARY:Weaver line: Planned Closure
UID:49f467f3-e2fe-41d4-a8ea-863d250e146c@49f4.org
